headline: Cencora Elects Lori J. Ryerkerk to Its Board of Directors
summary: CONSHOHOCKEN, Pa., May 28, 2025--Cencora, Inc. (NYSE: COR) today announced that its Board of Directors has elected Lori J. Ryerkerk as a new independent director, effective June 1, 2025.
